title: Goodwin: Hillary Faces Dangerous Enemy In The Obama Administration
text:
Goodwin: Hillary Faces Dangerous Enemy In The Obama Administration Published July 26, 2015 AP 
By Michael Goodwin, NY Post 
If Hillary Clinton were a cartoon character, she’d be Snidely Whiplash, forever muttering to herself, “Curses, foiled again.” And she’d be right.The lady in waiting will have to keep waiting. Probably forever. Fate has spoken.
